title: ‘I will prevent World War 3’, Trump says | AJ #shorts
description:
Republican presidential candidate Donald Trump said he would end the war in Ukraine, the conflict in the Middle East and prevent another World War from breaking out as he gave a campaign speech in Georgia on Tuesday.
